What is a tri-axis magnetic sensor?
A tri-axis magnetic sensor is a type of sensor that can measure magnetic fields along three perpendicular axes.

What are the key applications of tri-axis magnetic sensors?
Tri-axis magnetic sensors are used in various applications such as consumer electronics, automotive, industrial, and aerospace.

What are the main advantages of using tri-axis magnetic sensors?
The main advantages of using tri-axis magnetic sensors include their ability to provide 3D magnetic field measurement, compact size, and low power consumption.

